description: The First Trust Nasdaq Lux Digital Health Solutions ETF (the "Fund") seeks investment results that correspond generally to the price and yield (before the Fund's fees and expenses) of an equity index called the Nasdaq Lux Health Tech Index (the "Index"). The Fund will normally invest at least 80% of its net assets (plus any borrowings for investment purposes) in the common stocks and depositary receipts that comprise the Index.
name: First Trust Nasdaq Lux Digital Health Solutions ETF
